des:
The official voice app of the Philadelphia Eagles. You can ask for the latest podcast by series name or ask about the team. 

After you open the app, here are some things you can say.

- Play the latest Eagles Insider podcast
- Play the latest Eagle Eye In The Sky podcast
- Play the latest Journey To The Draft podcast

Be sure to check back later for the latest media from Eagles Entertainment.
